Summary: Disc rises from field and flies over home in MN.
divs: Sighting DetailsUnable to sleep, a woman was sitting in her livingroom when she heard a roaringsound. She observed a 30-foot disc rise from a nearby cornfield and fly quicklyover her roof. The object exterior was dark, with a ring of steady red lights.No other features were noted. She ran to another room and saw the object moveinto the distance, then "fade out" seemingly before being lost on the horizon.Total sighting duration was a matter of seconds.
